        "TileImage": "$($repository 11ec70e9-ebe6-43a7-bd73-f2135e00a115).Image",
        "Description": "&quot;What happens next will shock you!&quot;\r\rIt&apos;s well-known that journalism is one of the most dangerous professions, but did you know that motorsport journalism is four times as risky? Today, at least.\r\rI&apos;m not entirely convinced the public really believes the  whole &quot;journalist died in an accident&quot; stories, but if nothing else they&apos;re acclimated to them.\r\r\r= contract by ToeBeans (Steam) =",
